O_dJl5JzRkY3I_cSCWT5WqpJmr0gHTfLtSEX32w%26_nc_oc%3DAQnHm_9Zp-wdYfaBZPWjWDVRfS404YN98NB0qy3bCAqwd36Vfh9HE27OmR3le29S5WU%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D57c6d0f8d9a7a9f4c2284902b0085d9b%26oe%3D5DEEE528&h=c17c2b21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.15752-9/71038001_410574553220284_60605441700265984_n.png?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_eui2=AeGoygTSqvZaxoBRfxiA5dtMcNwcrA15PCHxWB7sVOND2AiepKGpRG5NGtRM9pqODZGcKv-77jcSdSjh4ed0a01wCaQk5XtL2q3j91R7pT-YCQ&amp;_nc_oc=AQmkq0cdCQqP5NQMr35AneJX6zYB8NeuWm_z4tJOXu_Y-UPWBa9vkCW1fzWNjqZuDcU&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=110bb659698729e3722a9ba45d5f31db&amp;oe=5E3992AC\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.15752-9%2F71038001_410574553220284_60605441700265984_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_eui2%3DAeGoygTSqvZaxoBRfxiA5dtMcNwcrA15PCHxWB7sVOND2AiepKGpRG5NGtRM9pqODZGcKv-77jcSdSjh4ed0a01wCaQk5XtL2q3j91R7pT-YCQ%26_nc_oc%3DAQmkq0cdCQqP5NQMr35AneJX6zYB8NeuWm_z4tJOXu_Y-UPWBa9vkCW1fzWNjqZuDcU%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D110bb659698729e3722a9ba45d5f31db%26oe%3D5E3992AC&h=8ec16c16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【十 &bull; 一國殤 ｜前哨戰烽火四起】<br />\n抗爭來到第113天，面對港共全方位的瘋狂打壓，我們或多或少都對現況感到氣餒。然而若我們放眼去看，其實反極權的戰線早已於全球各地展開&mdash;&mdash;不論是街頭抗爭還是國際鍵戰，我們期望每位香港人都能從中找到屬於自己的崗位。<br />\n就在美國國會即將於全體會議討論並投票表決《香港人權與民主法案》之際，香港人的首封公開信將率先於美國登場，同時，兩則電子廣告亦會於今天起在英國及歐盟成員國的報章網站發佈！身在外地的港人可留意以下的刊登時間，並把香港人的聲音帶到世界各地。<br />\n🇺🇸美國報章🇺🇸<br />\n🗓9月30日<br />\n🗞New York Times｜第5頁全版<br />\n🇪🇺歐盟成員國電子報🇪🇺*<br />\n🗓9月30日 及10月2日<br />\n💻POLITICO Europe<br />\n🇬🇧英國電子報🇬🇧*<br />\n🗓9月30日 至10月4日<br />\n💻Financial Times<br />\n*請先關閉封鎖網頁廣告的軟件<br />\n我們誠邀各位捕捉相關廣告並拍下照片，將其公開發佈至各社交媒體，再加上自己的訊息及標注 #GoodMourningCCP，呼籲全球與香港人一起集氣，對抗極權！<br />\n#FreedomHK #GoodMourningCCP #十一國殤日 #賀佢老母 #願榮光歸香港<br />\n-----⁣<br />\n有關眾籌活動的最新消息，可參閱以下的頻道。<br />\nFacebook 專頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/freedomhkgofficial\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffreedomhkgofficial&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6uoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=9545b95f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/freedomhkgofficial</a><br />\nTelegram Channel： <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/FreedomHKG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FFreedomHKG&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6uoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=b1083727\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/FreedomHKG</a><br />\nTwitter： <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/FreedomHKG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFreedomHKG&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6uoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=945075b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/FreedomHKG</a> <br />\nInstagram：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/freedomhkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ffreedomhkg&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6uoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=0d7b7c51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/freedomhkg</a>"},{"pid":"774b1e08e295366994f217e4fb3949da1f5f7c15","tid":1606071,"uid":29979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:58:54.000Z","msg":"大家聽日要有目標！唔好再賽跑啦！記得保護自己保護手足<br />\n<br />\n《終極軍師》勇武請入，十一「六區佔領政府部門」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605991</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f9efdd400ea4b5a624775352e9bc41d4a4afd55c","tid":1606071,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"774b1e08e295366994f217e4fb3949da1f5f7c15","tid":1606071,"uid":29979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:58:54.000Z","msg":"大家聽日要有目標！唔好再賽跑啦！記得保護自己保護手足<br />\n<br />\n《終極軍師》勇武請入，十一「六區佔領政府部門」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605991</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd1c83a1cb547ef121c705923728e3102dafdb1","tid":1606071,"uid":124048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371d0f81ec49cd1a6f66687effd4e9937f505ec3","tid":1606071,"uid":197243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:59:36.000Z","msg":"push <br />\n一諗到聽日個心好沉重"},{"pid":"b419bbbf1df052ccd0c0fbb191d4ba95d411b319","tid":1606071,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:59:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d554c8dff853666b0b51c03a829008a87e09cb10","tid":1606071,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:59:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日出去前睇左先</span></span></span><br />\n來自CSD職員既提醒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你班勇武手足,同我聽住,有部份前線手足認識我地,之前幾場戰役我地合作過,最初有人以為我地係鬼,詳細唔多講,我地係一班受過專業防暴訓練懲教署職員,之前已經係現場教過大家,如何組織防線同攻擊防暴,之前都有唔少進步,但今日我地冇出現,你地表現太差,中要咁多比人拉,我好心痛..<br />\n我地人手有限,身份問題,冇可能次次出現,我係度比些少資訊大家,希望大家務必share同發輝得好D<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.速龍都係人,佢地咩住咁重裝備同蒙面先至令信心大增,但大家留意下佢地人手一定唔夠手足多,只要大家穩固防線,只要佢地一跑出嚟,手足唔走向前攻,先用人火同磚頭攻,再快速向前推進, 趁機會足幾個差人抬去自己方向,呢個時候繼續用磚頭攻擊,同時向差人方向口射洗潔精地下,務別令佢地仆街,最重要立即除佢哋面具,之後私了..佢地以後就會驚..</span></span><br />\n2.佩槍唔係向上蚊,而係向內45度角向前推,大家明點做😁<br />\n3.如果執到警槍,同佢地玩過遊戲,逐粒子彈唔小心跌落坑渠,洗手間,包保玩殘佢地...<br />\n4.咁黑仔有狗用槍指你,可行情況試下用1秒用長竹,或雨傘打佢手同向上..<br />\n5如果打狗,唔該搵手足集中打腳,上半身有盾牌你打係冇用,要傷腳同關節先有足,以上除左增強攻擊同防護能力之外,就係要令到狗驚,你要記住佢地都係人,唔係超人...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6.哨兵必須去遠少少,手足唔好集足一個地方,必須快速移動,不停向唔同地方攻擊,切斷差人增援,攻擊完立即走人,玩殘班狗..</span></span><br />\n7.盡量引班狗去橋下,用高空方式攻擊..<br />\n最後10.1見,大家努力<br />\n一班CSD職員上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DLpdnBc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDLpdnBc.jpg&h=8ff53836&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aQC6HBd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaQC6HBd.jpg&h=3efa12b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f50ee0c8a63c135114ae33cf4ccb83fc617f3aa","tid":1606071,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:00:04.000Z","msg":"感謝攬炒巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f12edc1c0dd2f70a12abc9b816728a4be3d6f5","tid":1606071,"uid":292955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:00:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b11e5ae9357f67df4d5e7d452e914e414d86b29e","tid":1606071,"uid":242669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:01:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"53bc73f01f3a723189a5c6e4eaa8148ee65322fc","tid":1606071,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:03:15.000Z","msg":"多謝"},{"pid":"9fff40a50dfee9457e9d72a9b81e1f9f3b82dc05","tid":1606071,"uid":182061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:03:45.000Z","msg":"多謝"},{"pid":"a1a73d1474de8f6780ae57a76fab8d1088ebf0a4","tid":1606071,"uid":10484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:06:51.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"0f720b3698c8d1bcee3a8beaa0c5673702cdc44c","tid":1606071,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fd1c83a1cb547ef121c705923728e3102dafdb1","tid":1606071,"uid":124048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebab07b9cb661bb892645306073bf14bc9f7c11","tid":1606071,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"371d0f81ec49cd1a6f66687effd4e9937f505ec3","tid":1606071,"uid":197243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:59:36.000Z","msg":"push <br />\n一諗到聽日個心好沉重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fed8bd22430f918151cb2e25dfd28646d185f12","tid":1606071,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b419bbbf1df052ccd0c0fbb191d4ba95d411b319","tid":1606071,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:59:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7fdfc5b20f751516f0308b1f317f3ffc230652","tid":1606071,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d554c8dff853666b0b51c03a829008a87e09cb10","tid":1606071,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:59:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日出去前睇左先</span></span></span><br />\n來自CSD職員既提醒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你班勇武手足,同我聽住,有部份前線手足認識我地,之前幾場戰役我地合作過,最初有人以為我地係鬼,詳細唔多講,我地係一班受過專業防暴訓練懲教署職員,之前已經係現場教過大家,如何組織防線同攻擊防暴,之前都有唔少進步,但今日我地冇出現,你地表現太差,中要咁多比人拉,我好心痛..<br />\n我地人手有限,身份問題,冇可能次次出現,我係度比些少資訊大家,希望大家務必share同發輝得好D<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.速龍都係人,佢地咩住咁重裝備同蒙面先至令信心大增,但大家留意下佢地人手一定唔夠手足多,只要大家穩固防線,只要佢地一跑出嚟,手足唔走向前攻,先用人火同磚頭攻,再快速向前推進, 趁機會足幾個差人抬去自己方向,呢個時候繼續用磚頭攻擊,同時向差人方向口射洗潔精地下,務別令佢地仆街,最重要立即除佢哋面具,之後私了..佢地以後就會驚..</span></span><br />\n2.佩槍唔係向上蚊,而係向內45度角向前推,大家明點做😁<br />\n3.如果執到警槍,同佢地玩過遊戲,逐粒子彈唔小心跌落坑渠,洗手間,包保玩殘佢地...<br />\n4.咁黑仔有狗用槍指你,可行情況試下用1秒用長竹,或雨傘打佢手同向上..<br />\n5如果打狗,唔該搵手足集中打腳,上半身有盾牌你打係冇用,要傷腳同關節先有足,以上除左增強攻擊同防護能力之外,就係要令到狗驚,你要記住佢地都係人,唔係超人...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6.哨兵必須去遠少少,手足唔好集足一個地方,必須快速移動,不停向唔同地方攻擊,切斷差人增援,攻擊完立即走人,玩殘班狗..</span></span><br />\n7.盡量引班狗去橋下,用高空方式攻擊..<br />\n最後10.1見,大家努力<br />\n一班CSD職員上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DLpdnBc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDLpdnBc.jpg&h=8ff53836&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aQC6HBd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaQC6HBd.jpg&h=3efa12b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e4b8f26400aa63bc0540289964408bf8f59b2d","